Class AntPlusBikeSpdCadCommonPcc.IpcDefines

java.lang.Object
com.dsi.ant.plugins.antplus.pccbase.AntPlusBikeSpdCadCommonPcc.IpcDefines
Enclosing class:
AntPlusBikeSpdCadCommonPcc
public class AntPlusBikeSpdCadCommonPcc.IpcDefines extends Object
Defines the keys and values used to communicate between the PCC and plugin. User code should never have to reference these defines.
